flowchart TD
    Start([User Request]) --> Orchestrator[ORCHESTRATOR]

    
    Orchestrator --> Parse[1. Parse<br/>Phân tích]
    
    Parse --> Plan[2. Plan<br/>Đánh giá]
    
    Plan --> Classify{Simple?}
    
    %% Simple path
    Classify -->|Yes<br/>< 0.3| DirectLLM[Direct LLM<br/>Trả lời trực tiếp]
    DirectLLM --> Format
    
    %% Complex path
    Classify -->|No<br/>>= 0.3| Route{3. Route}
    
    Route -->|Cần tìm kiếm| Research[Research Agent<br/>Web + Documents]
    Route -->|Cần tính toán| Code[Code Agent<br/>Python execution]
    Route -->|Cần API| Tool[Tool Agent<br/>External APIs]
    
    Research --> Collect[4. Collect<br/>Thu thập]
    Code --> Collect
    Tool --> Collect
    
    Collect --> Validate{5. Validate<br/>OK?}
    
    Validate -->|Yes| Format[6. Format<br/>Định dạng]
    Validate -->|No| Retry{Retry?<br/>< 3}
    
    Retry -->|Yes| Route
    Retry -->|No| Fallback[Fallback]
    Fallback --> Format
    
    Format --> Response([Response])
    
    %% Error handling
    Research -.->|Error| ErrorHandler[Error<br/>Handler]
    Code -.->|Error| ErrorHandler
    Tool -.->|Error| ErrorHandler
    DirectLLM -.->|Error| ErrorHandler
    ErrorHandler -.-> Retry
    
    %% Monitoring
    State[(State)]
    Metrics[Metrics]
    
    Orchestrator -.-> State
    Route -.-> State
    Collect -.-> State
    
    Orchestrator -.-> Metrics
    Validate -.-> Metrics
    
    style Orchestrator fill:#FFE5E5,stroke:#FF6B6B,stroke-width:3px,color:#000
    style Classify fill:#E5F9FF,stroke:#00BCD4,stroke-width:3px,color:#000
    style DirectLLM fill:#E8F5E9,stroke:#4CAF50,stroke-width:3px,color:#000
    style Route fill:#E5F5FF,stroke:#2196F3,stroke-width:3px,color:#000
    style Validate fill:#E5FFE5,stroke:#8BC34A,stroke-width:3px,color:#000
    
    style Research fill:#E1F5FE,stroke:#03A9F4,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style Code fill:#E8EAF6,stroke:#5C6BC0,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style Tool fill:#FFF9C4,stroke:#FDD835,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    
    style Parse fill:#FFF3E0,stroke:#FF9800,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style Plan fill:#FFF9E5,stroke:#FFD93D,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style Format fill:#F3E5F5,stroke:#AB47BC,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style Collect fill:#FFE0B2,stroke:#FB8C00,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    
    style ErrorHandler fill:#FFEBEE,stroke:#EF5350,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style Retry fill:#FFF9C4,stroke:#FDD835,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
